nk a simple top could do that.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggX50r-F1f3_text","label":"ggX50r-F1f3_text","default":"<p>Olivia J.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga9ifit7kz_text","label":"gga9ifit7kz_text","default":"<p>Verified Buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIecaXd1H7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIecaXd1H7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiqGqP7jVp_text","label":"ggiqGqP7jVp_text","default":"<p>My Tops Finally Fit Right</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvOm1GF6hu_text","label":"ggvOm1GF6hu_text","default":"<p>Soft fabric, great fit, and no wires. My shoulders feel better and my tops finally sit right. Definitely buying more.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDWQKfSkTu_text","label":"ggDWQKfSkTu_text","default":"<p>Karine N.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg21WCNBJX4_text","label":"gg21WCNBJX4_text","default":"<p>Verified Buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwea36gd3F_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggwea36gd3F_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0kqiBWosj_text","label":"gg0kqiBWosj_text","default":"<p><strong>I Didn’t Think I’d Ever See This Lift Again</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg56Y3gCxIT_text","label":"gg56Y3gCxIT_text","default":"<p>I honestly thought I’d never see my chest look like this again. It feels lifted, supported, and natural — like my body in my 20s, but comfortable.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEXlXo6pOb_text","label":"ggEXlXo6pOb_text","default":"<p>Meggy J.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggt81-6qRlx_text","label":"ggt81-6qRlx_text","default":"<p>Verified Buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaR7iD5kxy_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaR7iD5kxy_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRcFobOsyx_text","label":"ggRcFobOsyx_text","default":"<p>This is what I wanted shapewear to be.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfXjbVnKDf_text","label":"ggfXjbVnKDf_text","default":"<p>Most shapewear made me look weird or created bulges. Elōa just makes my silhouette look clean and natural, like my body but upgraded.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_RjLn1yIv_text","label":"gg_RjLn1yIv_text","default":"<p>Marta C.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggui3ncSB5m_text","label":"ggui3ncSB5m_text","default":"<p>Verified Buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLQJTpP6k4_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggLQJTpP6k4_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi2_S5dYAi_text","label":"ggi2_S5dYAi_text","default":"<p>I look better in EVERY outfit now.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHI6suLSFf_text","label":"ggHI6suLSFf_text","default":"<p>Even my basic jeans + tee outfits look more flattering. My waist looks more defined and my top sits so much nicer on my body.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZYfcGr3Ek_text","label":"ggZYfcGr3Ek_text","default":"<p>Jade K.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVQb5cCw_c_text","label":"ggVQb5cCw_c_text","default":"<p>Verified Buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglbb0LRzeD_text","label":"gglbb0LRzeD_text","default":"<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.7</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>1897 Reviews.</u></strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOZcvbrPRE_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggOZcvbrPRE_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_554576614113936244-936f659e-1f7e-4287-ac81-ff34c91d32f6.svg"}],
